{"tid":684520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識得呢個人？","createTime":"2018-05-30T15:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T10:14:26.000Z","uid":81098,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8983dcf191315b59e6301d1b153ed55e737913f8","tid":684520,"uid":81098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/225704_90569879f27cbb178ab7b313a6eb9d57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F225704_90569879f27cbb178ab7b313a6eb9d57.png&h=cafc7774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/230138_db33e1c850a65f77162219f407b8620b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F230138_db33e1c850a65f77162219f407b8620b.png&h=d8e7cc79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個人呃左我朋友1萬蚊<br />\n佢聲稱自己阿婆入左醫院，之後話要做手術，下午5點幾個時話櫃員機只拎到2萬，仲差少少錢做手術<br />\n問我朋友借錢，話第二日會即刻還<br />\n我朋友好心見佢急住搵錢去幫佢阿婆，就借左比佢<br />\n之後佢就話佢阿婆過左身，忙住搞身後事，未得行過返錢比我朋友<br />\n過左幾日block埋我朋友電話，連打都打唔通<br />\n呢個人連工都唔返，成個人消失左<br />\n<br />\n佢叫楊子謙 Yeung Tsz Him<br />\n銀行戶口 775 191430668<br />\n佢電話係5687 7305<br />\n佢之前提過自己係住大埔，近廣福道<br />\n<br />\n有冇人見過佢/識得佢/知佢住邊？<br />\n如果你地識呢個人，真係要小心佢<br />\n作自己阿婆死，搵人借錢，之後走佬<br />\n我諗佢應該呃左唔少人，連份工作都唔要，成個人消失左<br />\n估唔到係香港做好人，無好報，就係呃你同情心"},{"pid":"765d0cae8985528748de31e939810bc48e92648b","tid":684520,"uid":81098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"大家如果見過呢個人/有佢資料/相，希望可以幫幫手，拎出黎"},{"pid":"9fbdf778ef4d1277f7c2b9517d1c0028911789f8","tid":684520,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"唔熟又借？"},{"pid":"e23cac4f3bee5ef16a1918a3ff859d23c154540f","tid":684520,"uid":81098,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9fbdf778ef4d1277f7c2b9517d1c0028911789f8","tid":684520,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1